## 4. Additional Assets

- Place your sample audio file at `frontend/assets/audio/sample.mp3`.
- For enhanced retro-neon aesthetics, consider importing Google Fonts like Orbitron and Press Start 2P in the `<head>` of `index.html`.

```html
<!-- Add to <head> in index.html -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
```

